      "updated": 1773215737424,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Outils CI :\n * Git (SCM)\n * framework de tests : xyzUnit, playwright\n * plateforme CI : \n      - azure devops\n      - Gitlab\n      - Github\n      - Jenkins\n\nFinalité des tests\n* brique robuste, fiable, maintenable\n* non regression\n* complétude, couverture\n* criticité",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Outils CI :\n * Git (SCM)\n * framework de tests : xyzUnit, playwright\n * plateforme CI : \n      - azure devops\n      - Gitlab\n      - Github\n      - Jenkins\n\nFinalité des tests\n* brique robuste, fiable, maintenable\n* non regression\n* complétude, couverture\n* criticité",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
